I tried to come out to my mom when I was fifteen and ended up taking it back because I was scared. Just said it was a phase. Now that I'm 24 and they've forced me to come out more or less, this is what's happened. Weirdly enough, I wanna live. For the first time, I'm more comfortable with myself and my life than I ever have been before. And I want my parents in my life, I do. But apparently they don't want me, so. I guess that's that.

The past month or so has been pretty hellish because of this. I've separated my finances from my parents and am planning to move out in a few months. I thought I could make this work but I can't. I just wanna be comfortable in my own skin. But I wanna live. And I guess I can't do that with them until I can get some space, at the least.

Thanks for reading. Please tell the queer people in your life that you love them. I have people that love and support me, but it's been a bit since I've seen em. Remind your loved ones.

Edit: thank you all so much for your love and support. I know I deserve love and happiness, sometimes it's just hard to see the light. I'm grateful for the reminder that i can get through this. I'm gonna look back on these comments on hard days, thank you so much ❤️❤️❤️</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/a9vGvXd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ahmackalak]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What species of primate is this?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Y9J55LZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fmAh3x2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Y9J55LZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WeirdAlisMySpiritUserName]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Meme dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/be5oFg0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CyeNDj1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My dog would still want closer</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4t3ynrl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WVLqt1v.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Love this. Uppy uppy</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o6wwwPK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J64lFd6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JKVJqAD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me too, bees.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H8t81SD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Agreed, skip intro was a game changer</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QWohdNT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>